{"tid":2421921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Now新聞台】匈牙利成首個使用國藥疫苗歐盟國家","createTime":"2021-02-25T00:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T06:57:54.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd1c2dad4db18839d50dacf4370f200ceb000b0","tid":2421921,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:31:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】匈牙利開始為民眾接種中國國藥的新冠病毒疫苗，是首個使用中國製疫苗的歐盟成員國。<br />\n<br />\n在匈牙利首都布達佩斯，醫護人員周三開始為民眾接種國藥疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n國藥疫苗是匈牙利第五款批准使用的新冠疫苗，較早時匈牙利政府承諾購買500萬劑國藥疫苗，可為250萬人接種，但有醫生擔心國藥疫苗的測試數據不足，當局是在政治壓力下批准使用國藥疫苗。當地早前亦有民調指，只有百分之27受訪者說，願意注射中國製疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>匈牙利總理歐爾班形容，開始接種國藥疫苗是匈牙利重要的一天。他較早時曾表示最信任中國製疫苗，又說會選擇注射國藥疫苗。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425225&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=fc1995dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425225&h=87cddacf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425225</a>"},{"pid":"4539c3ebe749c5b20ef147636909e2a1b17cb463","tid":2421921,"uid":91397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:32:00.000Z","msg":"歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4eb2cac6dfc923051f2eceeb8d1d2a50c2c019","tid":2421921,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4539c3ebe749c5b20ef147636909e2a1b17cb463","tid":2421921,"uid":91397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:32:00.000Z","msg":"歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"匈牙利一向奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c69125674b460ad7d79bf9bbda9429b1b28d1e9","tid":2421921,"uid":82640,"lik